OL,7,FA teenager, accused of the attempted
OL,8,Fmurder of two teachers and a pupil
OL,9,Fduring a school stabbing, told friends
OL,10,Fshe was "going to do something stupid"
OL,11,Fbefore the attack.
OL,13,FSwansea Crown Court today heard
OL,14,Fevidence from a pupil who said the
OL,15,Fdefendant had admitted she was going
OL,16,Fto do something "that will get me
OL,17,Fexpelled".
