OL,7,FTwo teachers and a pupil were injured
OL,8,Fduring the knife attack at Ysgol
OL,9,FDyffryn Aman, also known as Amman
OL,10,FValley School, in Ammanford.
OL,12,FThe 14-year-old defendant, who cannot
OL,13,Fbe identified for legal reasons, has
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to three counts of
OL,15,Fwounding with intent and one of
OL,16,Fpossession of a bladed article on
OL,17,Fschool premises.
