OL,7,FThe girl denies three counts of
OL,8,Fattempted murder in relation to the
OL,9,Fincident on April 24th this year, when
OL,10,Fshe was 13.
OL,12,FThe jury heard a police interview from
OL,13,Fthe pupil who described listening to
OL,14,Fthe defendant telling friends she was
OL,15,Fabout to do something "stupid" during
OL,16,Fa conversation in the school toilet.
