OL,7,FThe pupil said she believed the
OL,8,Fdefendant was "going to slap Ms Elias"
OL,9,Fbut was shocked when they realised the
OL,10,Fdefendant had attacked teacher Fiona
OL,11,FElias with a knife.
OL,13,FMs Elias suffered injuries to her arms
OL,14,Fand hand and required hospital
OL,15,Ftreatment after the attack.
OL,17,FThe court was also played a recording
OL,18,Fof evidence from a second pupil who
OL,19,Ftold how the defendant had sat with
OL,20,Fthem in the school hall on the morning
OL,21,Fof the attack.
