OL,7,FThe pupil said the defendant told her
OL,8,Fshe was "going to stab someone" before
OL,9,Fshowing them a knife.
OL,11,FThe pupil told officers during their
OL,12,Finterview: "I didn't believe her at
OL,13,Ffirst, but she showed us the knife, it
OL,14,Fhad a sliver blade with a tint of
OL,15,Fblue. She said she was going stab
OL,16,Fsomeone, I thought she was aiming it
OL,17,Fat Ms Elias.
