OL,7,FThe pupil said the defendant told him
OL,8,Fin the moments before the attack:
OL,9,F"This is going to be my last ever
OL,10,Fdrink, I'm going to do something, I'm
OL,11,Fgoing to be put away for a long time,
OL,12,FI'll make sure I get expelled."
OL,14,FHe added: "She took the knife out of
OL,15,Fher back pocket, it was like a
OL,16,Fbutterfly knife, that's when I got
OL,17,Fconcerned and thought we need to
OL,18,Fdistance ourselves from her and get
OL,19,Fout of the hall."
